রেতের বেলা একলা এখন
জিরচ্ছে সব শহরতলি,
চোখ দুটো খুব পড়ছে মনে
এই কথাটা কেমনে বলি?

সোনার চান্দ মোর, যাও দেখিয়া রে...

Those lines make the eyes filled with tears.

snippet.textDisplay: This rendition is out of this world,  in particular the bhawaiwa part. Sanai can gel with bhawiwa so exquisitely was  beyond my imagination. How come our folk songs can be so rich!! Our velvety green countryside with meandering rivers- may be!! So warm and vibrant with love and affection our country people as well are. Tears came out of my eyes- when I didn't even realise.  Heartiest congratulations to  the Team who have created this Masterpiece. Stay well. Stay blessed.
